title: Shock Doctor gómar
text:
Komnir í hús allt annað en intersport draslið… nokkur stykki eftir hægt að nálgast þá á æfinga tímum Fjölnis eða í gegnum PM.
Boil and bite to fit your mouth perfectly. Heavy-duty rubber Exoskeletal Shock Frame and Gel-Fit Liner provide maximum protection, fit and comfort in an easy to fit triple layer design. Breathing Channel allows for easy breathing while clenched.
Shock Doctor offers a free 10,000 insurance policy if anything ever happens to your teeth while wearing the GEL MAX
PROTECTS AGAINST CONCUSSIONS
